data.description: **Sellers are offering a 2.625% assumable VA loan option. Experience the best of single-level living in this exquisite all-brick ranch home, ideally located near Raleigh, NC. As you enter the welcoming foyer, you're greeted by a luminous, open-concept living area, seamlessly merging into a spacious kitchen. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring pristine white cabinets, elegant tile flooring, and high-quality granite countertops. The inviting eat-in bar is not just perfect for quick meals but also an excellent spot for hosting guests.    Every room of this home is adorned with crown molding, enhancing its sophistication, while the laminate hardwood flooring throughout the living spaces adds a touch of class. The luxurious owner's suite is a haven of comfort, complete with a stylish tray ceiling and an additional seating area for your private retreat.    Laundry chores are made effortless in the well-equipped laundry room, boasting a handy utility sink. Imagine unwinding on the covered porch, soaking in the serene open views that this property offers.    Situated just a short walk from the heart of downtown Benson, you'll enjoy convenient access to a variety of shops, restaurants, and local events, all adding to the small-town charm of the area. Outdoor enthusiasts will appreciate the proximity to nearby parks and trails, perfect for exploring the natural beauty of North Carolina.    This home is an ideal choice for those seeking a spacious, elegantly designed, and conveniently located residence near Raleigh, NC. Don't miss the chance to make this luxurious, convenient, and tranquil house your new home.
